This is Perl module JN::Life.

INSTALLATION

JN::Life installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

    % git clone git@github.com:Likk/JN-Life.git
    % cd JN-Life

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

JN::Life documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc JN::Life

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

